---
description: Use these rules whenever you create or edit UI tests
alwaysApply: false
---

- Playwright MCP is available for browser automation and inspection
- Frontend is running on `FRONTEND_URL` from `config/constants.ts`
- Always use `data-testid` based selectors (e.g., `page.getByTestId('login-submit-button')`)
- Once you complete a test, run the tests to verify they work as expected. In case of application bugs let me know about it.

